title: Disappointing
text: First of call it is COVID time so we ordered to go. We ordered seven items online and had instructions. No attention was given to the instructions. For example we wrote shredded chicken for the tacos and they completely missed it. We called and the lady at the reception was not even apologetic. We had to drive all the way back for their mistake because they don’t have delivery service. We didn’t have the time to reorder and that was disappointing.

title: disappointing
text: Perhaps it maybe the COVID time, we ordered a carryout and were extremely disappointed with the meal. It was smaller quantity, food was undercooked and very salty.

title: Unsure
text: We ordered Door Dash delivery. My son ordered Fajitas and they forgot to include tortillas. When we called back they sent another order. But i gave them 3 because the food was actually good. May be they just forgot to include tortillas with the Fajitas this one time. SO just let them know or remind them to add those when you call in.

title: Picturesque
text: The park has a beautiful castle which connects you to several trails. Just off to the next road there is a longer 6 mile hike for those interested in hiking.

title: Shopping and fun
text: Me and my daughter had a blast shopping in the many places here. We were at Coach, American Outfitters, Cosmetics company, cutlery shop and the lids.

title: Lovely cavern
text: This is a beautiful cavern with amazing formations. The tour was quite informative and detailed. This is a must see.

title: CREPES
text: Its the best Italian buffet you can enjoy starting with salads which includes hash browns to the pastas and pizzas at various stations. The entire dessert menu is available to choose from. The crepes are the best and always have long line but never miss tasting them. They are made to your options or choice of topping. We were there before COVID so i am not sure about the temp checks etc. Sorry

title: More for your money
text: Shagan’s feels like you are at home! The food is authentic. Anything you order here, you find the best quality there is. Neither spicy nor too mild!

title: Very good
text: Took Air India from Mumbai to Newark. The flight was pleasant, felt that there was enough leg room and comfort even on a very packed flight. As always the customer service is great.

title: Nice
text: Nice beach area to stroll, work out and enjoy a walk by the shore. Beware of the "man of war" here. Several are washed up the shore and some are even alive. We tried putting some back into the ocean.

title: Very nice
text: We had reservation for a room with two queen beds. Since the hotel was under renovation, we were offered two separate rooms at no additional cost. We checked very late and the lady at the desk was very nice. Am glad we weren't turned away or shoved into a smaller room to accommodate. The breakfast was okay (not bad). Rooms were very clean.
place: Holiday Inn Express Hotel & Suites Jacksonville - Mayport / Beach
